   224	        # A single diverged snapshot (u=1e30) would otherwise contaminate the
   225	        # percentile-clipped mean. MAD-based filtering is scale-invariant and
   226	        # doesn't require a hand-tuned physics band.
   227	        median = float(np.median(values_finite))
